HEADWORD: Captaincy
<hw>Cap"tain*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<er>Captaincies</er> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <def>The rank, post, or
